{"word":"Jerimoth","slug":"jerimoth","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jerimoth</b> <a href=\"#/H3406\">H3406</a> <br/> 1. Called Jeremoth, son of Bela<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=7&verse=7'>1Ch 7:7</a><br/> 2. Son of Becher<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=7&verse=8'>1Ch 7:8</a><br/> 3. A disaffected Israelite, who denounced Saul and joined David at Ziklag<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=5'>1Ch 12:5</a><br/> 4. Son of Mushi<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=23'>1Ch 23:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=24&verse=30'>1Ch 24:30</a><br/> 5. Son of Heman<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=25&verse=4'>1Ch 25:4</a><br/> 6. A ruler of the tribe of Naphtali<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=19'>1Ch 27:19</a><br/> 7. A son of David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=18'>2Ch 11:18</a>"}]}